"   <div class=\"block pha drugH1Div\" id=\"F158827\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Mechanism of Action",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Decreases the sensitivity of cough receptors and interrupts cough impulse transmission by depressing the medullary cough center through sigma receptor stimulation; structurally related to codeine",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block phk drugH1Div\" id=\"F158838\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
